      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLYING MONKEY'S (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with nine wins and nine minors from 23 tries. Placed last time (22.86) at this track in a NG, finishing third and beaten 1.5 lengths. Has the ability and should feature. DIVA'S DELIGHT (2) is in hot form winning her last four on end, the latest pinging the lids with a sensational early split and clocking 22.75 over 400m at this track. Has good early burn and is drawn to be prominent. Leading player again. JOCK (7) turned in a solid run fresh when finishing in the placings at Gunnedah in a NG (20.15). Solid record at the distance winning 10 races. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Likely to be in the finish again. SMART COMET (3) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
